  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age â‰¥16 years

          -  Underlying haematological malignancy

          -  Planned allogeneic peripheral blood stem cell transplantation from a 10/10 or 9/10 HLA
             matched unrelated donor, using an Alemtuzumab-based conditioning protocol

          -  Written Informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Life expectancy &lt; 6 weeks

          -  Female patients who are pregnant and lactating

          -  Patients who are serologically positive for Hepatitis B, C or HIV pre-SCT
      </textblock>
